ji\" /> <br />\n不過今個演唱會 冇遙吻 無能為力 真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe0fd6cc1df329cd92b6125bf15edf06851d27d","tid":703443,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321ae706e48743250eb08c74fa2528392d80fc37","tid":703443,"uid":144268,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb3a21935c4b8fe1da4627b8819a1297ddf12ab5","tid":703443,"uid":143116,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T22:01:33.000Z","msg":"反而覺得佢女裝係解放咗佢其中一部分係自己<br />\n雖然我知地位上冇得比較，但係估唔到十八年前張國榮女裝俾人鬧，十八年後香港人都係冇進步過"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T22:41:03.000Z","msg":"真心覺得無問題 <br />\nGolando個gimmick搵到錢 fan屎聽得玩得開心都無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T22:47:02.000Z","msg":"佢果個Gonlando網上直播live show 果次都做得好好<br />\n我覺得佢翻唱人歌 係網上做個live concert 賣感情ok<br />\n但fans等左4年既自己演唱會竟然都唱咁多人地歌 自己原汁原味既歌冇左"},{"pid":"c0ddb512a45ea36c12c989fa73441b9732a08226","tid":703443,"uid":4933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T22:50:44.000Z","msg":"觸摸心跳好正，樓豬識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前嘅皇上冇可能返嚟，<br />\n此終人大了，有更多唔同諗法，<br />\n到咗依個年紀，<br />\n佢認該會清楚自己條音樂路點行，<br />\n作為十多年嘅粉絲，我會支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cd345ba5f8c24acedf86a0bb86c00888c1c81c","tid":703443,"uid":82917,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T23:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/065148_5532efe942b8b3fbf269d527976571bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F065148_5532efe942b8b3fbf269d527976571bc.png&h=940c037a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/065150_90a19cdd3d8979288f100302ee394057.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F1